otherNames: Sorcerous Stabber Orphen -Chaos in Urbanrama-, Majutsushi Orphen Hagure Tabi: Urbanrama-hen, 魔術士オーフェンはぐれ旅 アーバンラマ編
synopsis:
Third season of Majutsushi Orphen Hagure Tabi.

After the events of Kimluck, Orphen is on a quest to find Azalie, only to find himself in a war in between celestial beings and humans.
